--------------------------------
       PYTHON WEBSERVER 
--------------------------------
1) mkdir cgi-bin
2) cd    cgi-bin
3) touch Hello.py


print('Content-Type: text/html')
print( '<html>')
print( '<head></head>')
print( '<body>')
print( '<h2>Hello World</h2>')
print( '</body></html>')

Lamccia il programma 

python -m http.server 80000 --cgi

Nel browser scrivi 

localhost:80000/cgi-bin/Hello.py

